• Define the new state-of-the-art for machine learning engineering in the road logistics services;
• Prototype and subsequently operationalize innovative, data-intensive, end-to-end machine-learning-based decision engines, following the latest best practices on MLOps;
• Outline and develop health and performance monitoring tools (MLOps) of data pipelines and the machine learning services in production;
• Design and improve heterogeneous, asynchronous and high-performance large-data processing pipelines from/to multiple sources/destinations;
