At Universität Tübingen we are looking for a ML, AI engineer!

🛠️ Our tech stack:
CSS, GitHub, Grafana, HTTP, Java, JavaScript, Jenkins, Linux, Machine Learning, PyTorch, Python, Web, Machine-Learning

